rooms.desc: A arrow trap, making a faint clicking sound nearby.
A warg prowling near the entrance.
A swinging axe, cleverly disguised as safe ground.
A crystal coffer, sealed with ancient runes.
A hidden fountain, filled with soft candlelight.
A ancient chest, sealed with ancient runes.
A abandoned camp, still warm from a previous traveler.
A shadow knight patrolling a mossy hallway.
